                                       FLR - 960222
                                       
  /al/reference/gal 
  ===================

  contains machine independant files.

  README   - this file
 
  Makefile - redo a galeph module with the current versions
           

  tpciii.news    gives the changes compare to previous version

  srctpciii      directory source file of tpcsim version # iii



 /aleph/gal/ directory
  ====================

  contains galeph and tpcsim libraries and various links to the
  sources.

  README           link to /al/reference/gal/README

  Makefile         link to /al/reference/gal/Makefile
                   makefile to link galeph
                   it uses the following environment variables:
                   ALEPH, OS, FC, FCOPT, UNDEF, GUSER
                   it includes the /aleph/gal/galeph.version file. 

  galeph.version   current galeph version number = $galver

  galeph           galeph module, current version
   
  galeph.news      link to $ALROOT/galiii/news/news.h
                   what has changed between version # iii and
                   previous one.

  galeph.cards     link to /al/reference/gal/galeph.cards
                   an example of data cards to be customized.

  gmain.o          link to /aleph/gal/gmainiii.o
                   main program for current galeph version
  
  libgaleph.a      link to /aleph/gal/libgaliii.a, _dbx.a
  libgaleph_dbx.a  galeph libraries, version # iii

  srcgaleph        link to $ALROOT/galiii/

  tpcsim.version   tpcsim current version number = $tpcver
     
  tpcsim.news      link to $ALROOT/tpckkk/news/news.h
                   what has changed between version # kkk and
                   previous one.

  libtpcsim.a      link to /aleph/gal/libtpckkk.a, _dbx.a
  libtpcsim_dbx.a  tpcsim libraries, version # kkk.


 ======

  $ALROOT/galnnn
  ==============

  galnnn.input   | used to build the galeph library
  galnnn.job     | /aleph/gal/libgalnnn.a , _dbx.a

  inc/             include files
  calo/ to vdet/   source files
  news/            news

  $ALROOT/tpciii
  ==============

  tpciii.input   | used to build the tpcsim library
  tpciii.job     | /aleph/gal/libtpciii.a, _dbx.a

  inc/             include files
  F77/             source files
  news/            news
  

 
 
